name: Tetracyclines
title: Tetracyclines
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values includes select antibiotics that are Tetracyclines. Including oral and IV formulations.),(Data Element Scope: This data element intend to identify patients who are on Tetracyclines antibiotics),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes that represent Tetracyclines antibiotics  and any that has the ingredients as Tetracyclines: demeclocycline, doxycycline, eravacycline, minocycline, omadacycline, sarecycline, tetracycline, tigecycline.),(Exclusion Criteria: Otic, Topical and Ophthalmic formulation)
